# DiscoveryOne -- .gitignore
#
# IMPORTANT: .agentrail/ and .agentrail-archive/ are tracked
# source-of-record. They MUST NEVER be added to this file.
# Every saga step's commit must include the .agentrail/ delta;
# every archive operation must commit both the cleared
# .agentrail/ and the populated .agentrail-archive/. See
# CLAUDE.md "Rules for `.agentrail/`" for the full protocol.
#
# If you find yourself reaching to ignore .agentrail/, stop and
# read CLAUDE.md first. Direct deletion of unstaged step files
# is unrecoverable.

# Rust build output.
target/
**/*.rs.bk

# Trunk / wasm-pack output for the web app.
dist/
ui/web/dist/
ui/web/pkg/

# reg-rs transient state (databases and locks). The .rgt and
# .out baselines ARE tracked. Cargo.lock is also tracked
# (binary-crate convention) so this glob is intentionally
# narrow: only reg-rs *.tdb / *.tdb.lock are ignored.
**/*.tdb
**/*.tdb.lock

# Generated WASM and intermediate compile outputs.
work/generated/

# OS / editor cruft.
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
